Waffles (C++) :
	- Installing :
		> git clone https://github.com/mikegashler/waffles.git waffles
		> cd waffles/src
		> sudo make install

	- Running : (in waffles/src and make sure the .arffFile is in waffles/src too)
		> waffles_learn train (.arffFile) decisiontree > (outputFile1) # For creading the tree
		> waffles_plot printdecisiontree (outputFile1) (.arffFile) > (outputFile2) # Shows the tree in a readable format

	- Class Reference: 
		http://uaf46365.ddns.uark.edu/waffles/apidoc/html/class_g_classes_1_1_g_decision_tree.html#a261f02b06147d7d2bfe5e6ed7b7ca3c8

Weka (Java) :
	- Installing :
		http://www.cs.waikato.ac.nz/ml/weka/downloading.html (weka-3-8-0.zip) and unzip.

	- Running :
		> java -jar weka.jar
		> Click on SimpleCLI
		> In the new terminal type java weka.classifiers.trees.J48 -t ./data/iris.arff > outputFile

Other libraries : 
http://www.mlpack.org/
http://dlib.net/

